quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  16,1,"Allah's judgement has (all but) come; do not, then, call for its speedy advent. Holy is He, and far above their associating others with Him in His Divinity.",footnotes:178660:1,footnotes:178661:2
  16,2,"He sends down this spirit(of prophecy) by His command through His angels on any of His servants whom He wills, (directing them): "Warn people that there is no deity but Me; so hold Me alone in fear."",footnotes:178662:1,footnotes:178663:2,footnotes:178664:3
  16,3,"He created the heavens and the earth with Truth. Exalted is He above whatever they associate with Allah in His Divinity.",footnotes:178665:1
  16,4,"He created man out of a mere drop of fluid, and lo! he turned into an open wrangler.",footnotes:178666:1
  16,5,"He created the cattle. They are a source of clothing and food and also a variety of other benefits for you."
  16,6,"And you find beauty in them as you drive them to pasture in the morning and as you drive them back home in the evening;"